{
  "stem": "21978.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So we enrolled ourselves into a board-- into a nursing school, which had a boarding-- it was a boarding school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was attached to a hospital run by nuns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were taught by nuns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were taught by doctors and nurses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we were there for our-- during our training.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we had to work very hard in the hospital, and we had to study.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we have been really different from the other girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "None of them was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were all young Jewish-- girls, from the country, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And when they were very upset that they have to be here without their mothers or something, we were telling them, don't be stupid.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But I remember that we didn't tell them much about our experiences because they were not interested.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "When we came back, we found out that people didn't want to hear much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They had their own worries during the Hitler regime, during the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They liked to be talking about their own problems, and didn't want to hear about others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Or we didn't talk to them because we thought they wouldn't believe us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because it was so unbelievable, even to us, that we survived, that we went through it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And then we didn't want to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We thought-- just thought we will forget about everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we studied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we-- we nursed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we had a lot of fun, also, because Annetta and I, we looked the same in the uniform, nurses' uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We looked the same, and people were-- were mixing us up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "That Annetta was working in one department, and when she finished, I went in there, and nobody knew that I am different.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
